'''丁型流感病毒'''（英文：Influenza D virus）是一种[[流感病毒|流感病毒]]，也是[[正黏液病毒科|正黏液病毒科]]丁型流感病毒屬（Deltainfluenzavirus）中的一[[种|种]]，可引起[[流行性感冒|流行性感冒]]。丁型流感病毒可感染[[猪属|猪]]和[[家牛|牛]]，但尚未有人受感染的报道。<ref name="Influenza D2">{{cite journal|title=Novel Influenza D virus: Epidemiology, pathology, evolution and biological characteristics|date=25 August 2017|journal=Virulence|issue=8|doi=10.1080/21505594.2017.1365216|volume=8|pages=1580–1591|pmc=5810478|pmid=28812422|author3=Gairu Li|author4=Fiona Kerlin|author5=Michael Veit|author1=Shuo Su|author2=Xinliang Fu}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Types of Influenza Viruses|url=https://www.cdc.gov/flu/about/viruses/types.htm|accessdate=2021-01-06|date=2019-11-18|last=CDC|work=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121163152/https://www.cdc.gov/flu/about/viruses/types.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Emerging Influenza D Virus Threat: What We Know so Far!|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30764577/|last=Asha|first=Kumari|last2=Kumar|first2=Binod|date=2019-02-05|journal=Journal of Clinical Medicine|issue=2|doi=10.3390/jcm8020192|volume=8|issn=2077-0383|pmc=6406440|pmid=30764577|access-date=2021-01-06|archive-date=2022-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220127094520/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30764577/}}</ref> 与[[甲型流感病毒|甲型]]、[[乙型流感病毒|乙型]]、[[丙型流感病毒|丙型]]感染比较，丁型流感病毒的感染病例较不常见，截止目前还没有人体的针对性[[疫苗|疫苗]]。<ref name="Influenzavirus C and D2">{{cite web|title=Influenza C and Influenza D Viruses|url=https://www.swinehealth.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Influenza-virus-C-IVC-and-influenza-virus-D-IVD.pdf|author=2016|access-date=28 September 2018|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213828/https://www.swinehealth.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Influenza-virus-C-IVC-and-influenza-virus-D-IVD.pdf}}</ref>

2011年，丁型流感病毒首次从猪身上被分离，2016年被正式确认为正黏液病毒科的一个[[属|属]]，不同于[[丙型流感病毒|丙型流感病毒]]的属（此前曾有一段时间被认为是丙型病毒的一种亚型）。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":0">{{cite journal|title=Isolation of Influenza C Virus from Pigs and Experimental Infection of Pigs with Influenza C Virus|author=|url=|journal=Journal of General Virology|issue=|doi=10.1099/0022-1317-64-1-177|others=|year=1983|volume=64|page=|pages=177–82|pmid=6296296|author3=Wang P.|author4=Wang M.|author5=Zhu J.M.|author1=Guo Y.|author2=Jin F.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=New virus gets official name, influenza D|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/09/160901140433.htm|accessdate=2021-01-06|work=ScienceDaily|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213939/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/09/160901140433.htm}}</ref> 与丙型病毒一样，丁型病毒拥有7个单链[[RNA|RNA]]片段，而甲型和乙型则拥有8个单链RNA片段。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Influenza C and D Viruses Package Eight Organized Ribonucleoprotein Complexes|url=https://jvi.asm.org/content/92/6/e02084-17|last=Nakatsu|first=Sumiho|last2=Murakami|first2=Shin|date=2018-03-15|journal=Journal of Virology|issue=6|doi=10.1128/JVI.02084-17|volume=92|language=en|issn=0022-538X|pmid=29321324|last3=Shindo|first3=Keiko|last4=Horimoto|first4=Taisuke|last5=Sagara|first5=Hiroshi|last6=Noda|first6=Takeshi|last7=Kawaoka|first7=Yoshihiro|access-date=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308075350/https://jvi.asm.org/content/92/6/e02084-17}}</ref> 丁型与丙型大约有50%的[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]组成相似，二者均无亚型/支系分类。<ref name="Influenza D2" /><ref name="Influenzavirus C and D2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=流感高发！关于流感病毒你应该知道的N个真相！|url=http://www.ioz.cas.cn/kxcb/kpwz/201801/t20180116_4934511.html|accessdate=2021-01-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=中国科学院动物研究所|language=|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213905/http://www.ioz.cas.cn/kxcb/kpwz/201801/t20180116_4934511.html}}</ref>

